 was taking place time and again in the district. Appealing to the party leaders and cadres of the party to take humanitarian responsibility as rescue and relief work at this tragic hour, NC President Deuba wished for eternal peace of the departed soul and extended condolences on bereaved families.","title":"NC President Deuba expresses grief over Sindhupalchowk disaster","url":"http://english.ratopati.com/story/15264","video":[]}
